0a0da82b72b2c6b52b3e00bad7e2.png&h=09c908cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n定對於洗版行為認為係好好玩？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/075340_8c4008eb4004f93aa46023e030459e7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F075340_8c4008eb4004f93aa46023e030459e7e.png&h=b0cbfac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n輕輕鬆鬆吹水咪吹水 姐係傾計 <br />\n交友定其他發展 係後續嘅事 唔明你點解唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我只見字都未打好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/080000_661789d69dc4e7c9fb5a7f4d25987276.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F080000_661789d69dc4e7c9fb5a7f4d25987276.png&h=26bc83ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為誤會左 所有入黎就自貼？定係...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/080246_580ecfe9f9050225a57c3f2535e1f87a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F080246_580ecfe9f9050225a57c3f2535e1f87a.png&h=b073ff17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n定係依然覺得騷擾及攻擊其他人為樂？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/080544_49690cdc66b193655688787452a6beaf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F080544_49690cdc66b193655688787452a6beaf.png&h=0b6a3ad4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者我咁講 <br />\n<br />\n此 吹水谷為萍水相逢的人閒時放低幾句 瘋狂幾句<br />\n但我認為你地嘅行為係有目的性進入並作攻擊/嬉戲 <br />\n<br />\n多翻勸告無用 <br />\n圖中會員則會永不歡迎在此群組"},{"pid":"bb78f92d219081ef2557bd34489466447ab4b732","tid":588724,"uid":154471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e4c96b1ef328c4dafbd998cdd5ed96154e653ba","tid":588724,"uid":3218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a85f341e31c2976775dea9376d7646743c403bcb","tid":588724,"uid":154471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5afe53b8bf43bff261d948584c09d592ce935399","tid":588724,